data.description: BETTER THAN NEW!!  Welcome to the Woodland Village by Lifestyle Homes.  This community was designed with family, friends and play in mind.  This gorgeous and IMMACULATE One story, three bedroom, two bath plus three car garage is fully landscaped with many upgrades and is just two years old.   Open concept living and kitchen with Granite countertops in kitchen, luxury vinyl planking all through the house except bedrooms, laundry room with cabinets. RV PARKING!  Cement rear patio and three car garage with one bay “pull through” for ease in pulling through a boat or small trailer to the backyard. This home is located on a premium corner lot with RV gate on side for ease of RV parking.  Weed block installed under front and rear landscaping.   Pride in ownership throughout home. Many of the doors are trimmed with an upgraded shaker style.    All you need to do is MOVE IN.   Walk along the miles of paved walking trails, take those furry  babies to the fully fenced five acre dog park, kids will love the three parks and a Family Center with lots of activities.  Direct BLM land access – close to many outdoor destinations and activities.   Woodland Village, located about 17 highway miles to downtown Reno, currently includes 2,200 single family detached homes, 110 attached townhomes (under construction), 3 Washoe County parks, 2 schools, a non-profit family and fitness center with childcare, a small neighborhood commercial center, including a family-friendly restaurant, over 10 miles of landscaped walking trails and several direct access points to the surrounding BLM lands as well as a multitude of other outdoor recreational locations and activities. provide a beautiful and safe tree-lined community nestled into the Cold Springs Valley, which is surrounded by stunning mountain views.
